      "id": "d8759581_352f06cc",
      "file_path": "sources/hv-collector-main/src/main/kotlin/org/onap/dcae/collectors/veshv/main/servers/HealthCheckServer.kt",
      "patchset_number": 8,
      "line": 34,
      "message": "It can't be moved as Metrics are used in it and moving all of that is not scope of this task.\n\nNote that all this class does is delegates to factory.HealthCheckApiServer, starts server and logs it. \nTBH it's so small that I don't see benefit in moving or changing it.",
